      <description>&lt;p&gt;д»ҘдёӢжҳҜ Obsidian е®ҳж–№ CLI зҡ„иҜҰз»Ҷд»Ӣз»Қпјҡ&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;obsidian-cli--е®ҳж–№е‘Ҫд»ӨиЎҢз•Ңйқў&#34;&gt;Obsidian CLI вҖ” е®ҳж–№е‘Ҫд»ӨиЎҢз•Ңйқў&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;д»Җд№ҲжҳҜ-obsidian-cli&#34;&gt;д»Җд№ҲжҳҜ Obsidian CLIпјҹ&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Obsidian CLI жҳҜдёҖдёӘе‘Ҫд»ӨиЎҢз•ҢйқўпјҢи®©дҪ еҸҜд»Ҙд»Һз»Ҳз«ҜжҺ§еҲ¶ ObsidianпјҢз”ЁдәҺи„ҡжң¬зј–еҶҷгҖҒиҮӘеҠЁеҢ–е’ҢдёҺеӨ–йғЁе·Ҙе…·йӣҶжҲҗгҖӮ &lt;a href=&#34;https://releasebot.io/updates/obsidian&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;  class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;&gt;Releasebot&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt; Obsidian е®ҳж–№еңЁ 2026 е№ҙ 2 жңҲ 27 ж—ҘжӯЈејҸеҗ‘жүҖжңүз”ЁжҲ·жҺЁйҖҒдәҶ 1.12 зүҲжң¬пјҢе…¶дёӯеҢ…еҗ«иҝҷдёҖеҠҹиғҪгҖӮ &lt;a href=&#34;https://x.com/obsdmd&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;  class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;&gt;X&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
